{"tid":1145972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【矚目奶奶】着「婚紗」赴兒子婚宴滿場飛 親友看不過眼拍照公審","createTime":"2019-05-09T03:11:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T10:39:39.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"92c016437897bdaa27df36599cdc614b870bf3ba","tid":1145972,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T03:11:15.000Z","msg":"結婚是人生大事，新娘當然希望成為婚禮焦點，可惜外國這場婚宴焦點勢必落在新娘子的奶奶身上&mdash;&mdash;她竟穿一條類似婚紗款式的白色禮服裙赴宴，還滿場飛與賓客拍照，有親友看不過眼，拍下照片放上網公審。<br />\n「大家看看，這是我丈夫的姨姨出席自己兒子婚禮的裝束，這位女士，你在做甚麼？」相片的說明這樣寫道，相片可見，身材仍然火辣、風韻猶存的金髮奶奶身穿一條白色低胸禮服裙赴宴，修腰的剪裁加上那裙子的魚尾裙擺非常浮誇，非常矚目。她風騷地抱着花女拍照，又跟新娘的姊妹合照，令人乍看還以為她才是新娘。<br />\n那麼新娘穿得更浮誇嗎？倒不是。從這位親友上載的相片可見，皮膚較黝黑的新娘穿的裙子款式，跟其奶奶的十分相似，胸前的剪裁幾乎一模一樣，裙擺看來甚至不及奶奶的華麗。不過上載者無提及新娘看到奶奶裝束時的反應。<br />\n相片放上facebook「以婚禮為恥」的群組，隨即一石激起千層浪，有人形容「真是一個可憐的注意力尋求者」，有人附和說：「太奇怪了吧！」有人更放狠話說：「要有多精神失常，才會在兒子的婚禮上穿得像新娘子？」不少人更建議應趕她離開，也有人說：「她穿的裙子剪裁跟新娘子的幾乎一樣，真混亂，她那麼火辣，其實穿其他甚麼也可以吧！」不過也有人力撐她說：「說實話，如果我仍然那麼火辣，我也許也會這樣做。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190508/large/1557301822_88db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190508%2Flarge%2F1557301822_88db.jpg&h=02de7aa4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n猜猜誰是新娘？誰是奶奶？<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190508/large/1557301822_8e79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190508%2Flarge%2F1557301822_8e79.jpg&h=0da7e57f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開估：這是奶奶<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190508/large/1557301822_8ea1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190508%2Flarge%2F1557301822_8ea1.jpg&h=df0ac636&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這位奶奶還滿場飛與姊妹合照<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190508/large/1557301824_e2c7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190508%2Flarge%2F1557301824_e2c7.jpg&h=7f9435f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網民留言批評奶奶搶新抱風頭<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190509/59576758\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190509%2F59576758&d=fyMqA0bs77BZF9qEbHCyfstxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=14c1ad8c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190509%2F59576758&h=eb1f9142\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190509/59576758</a>"},{"pid":"8f54349c7e17c0798864f45df105a8ea1b811a43","tid":1145972,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T03:18:06.000Z","msg":"亂倫一定有"},{"pid":"ac147af95375cc2f04b1bf563e896d0d34c73851","tid":1145972,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f54349c7e17c0798864f45df105a8ea1b811a43","tid":1145972,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T03:18:06.000Z","msg":"亂倫一定有"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T03:19:47.000Z","msg":"宣示主權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打正旗號同個仔影婚紗相"},{"pid":"6fa0929908c6b6af0726965f11db5841806ac7f8","tid":1145972,"uid":152123,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T03:32:05.000Z","msg":"啲痴線奶奶真係乞人憎到極致 不分國藉"},{"pid":"0a77709efcca5ae777dbd69c6643d8fe1f9f550b","tid":1145972,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac147af95375cc2f04b1bf563e896d0d34c73851","tid":1145972,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f54349c7e17c0798864f45df105a8ea1b811a43","tid":1145972,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T03:18:06.000Z","msg":"亂倫一定有"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T03:19:47.000Z","msg":"宣示主權<img src=\"/assets/fa